      "rationale": "Use error is scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device where model influence is Medium and independent testing confirms CFD results. The simulation workflow is executed by a single experienced CFD analyst using a validated template; no user-to-user variability study is warranted at this risk level. ASME V&V 40 Table 1 does not require a Use Error assessment at Gradation 2 for MRL 2 contexts with corroborating experimental data."
