      "rationale": "Test samples factor is scoped out because all validation experiments used a single FDA generic centrifugal blood pump specimen fabricated to nominal drawing dimensions. Device-to-device geometric variability is addressed separately through the parametric CFD tolerance study that forms the core COU deliverable. Requiring a multi-specimen experimental campaign would duplicate effort already covered by the computational sensitivity analysis and is not required at MRL 2 Gradation 2."
